    ("3.2.2e", "Include practical exercises in awareness training that are aligned with current threat scenarios and provide feedback to individuals involved in the training and their supervisors", "3.2 Awareness and Training"),
    ("3.3.1e", "Deploy an audit record generation capability that provides an organization-defined level of auditing of user-level and system-level activities that supports real-time alerting and analysis", "3.3 Audit and Accountability"),
    ("3.4.1e", "Establish and maintain an authoritative source and repository to provide a trusted source and accountability for approved and implemented system components", "3.4 Configuration Management"),
    ("3.4.2e", "Employ automated mechanisms to detect misconfigured or unauthorized system components and place components that cannot be remediated into a quarantine or remediation network", "3.4 Configuration Management"),
    ("3.4.3e", "Employ automated discovery and management tools to maintain an up-to-date, complete, accurate, and readily available inventory of system components", "3.4 Configuration Management"),
    ("3.5.1e", "Identify and authenticate systems and system components, where possible, before establishing a network connection using bidirectional authentication that is cryptographically-based and replay-resistant", "3.5 Identification and Authentication"),
